<p>Easy enough!</p>
<p>In the <code>product/</code> directory create that template: <code>new.html.twig</code>. Extend the base
layout - <code>layout.html.twig</code> - and add add a <code>body</code> block. Add a <code>form</code> tag and make
it submit right back to this same URL with <code>method="POST"</code>:</p>
