<p>Bug fixed! Try it:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/product_admin.feature:19</div></code></pre>
<p>It's green! In fact, we can go to the browser, refresh and see the Veloci-chew toy
for $20.</p>
<p>But there's a problem: it says that the author is "anonymous". This should be "admin"
since I created it under that user. That's definitely a bug: we forgot to set the
author in <code>ProductAdminController</code>. Ok, we know how to fix bugs using BDD: add a
step to prove the bug:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="592adb51ac">
