<p>This is safe because there should only be the <em>1</em> product in the list. Back over
to the terminal and run the test:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/product_admin.feature:19</div></code></pre>
<p>Yes! The new step fails, phew!</p>
